/* MARK: - Setup Guide Instructions */
"Open Cutling in your device's **Settings** app." = "ଆପଣଙ୍କ ଡିଭାଇସର **ସେଟିଂସ** ଆପରେ କଟ୍‌ଲିଂ ଖୋଲନ୍ତୁ।";
